  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatMessageCreatedEvent
    Event fired when a chat message is created.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/ChatMessageCreated
    ChatMessageDeletedEvent
    Event fired when a chat message is deleted.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/ChatMessageDeleted
    ChatMessageUpdatedEvent
    Event fired when a chat message is updated.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/ChatMessageUpdated
    GuildedEvent
    Basic unprocessed Guilded WebSocket event.
    GuildedWebSocketClosedEvent
    Event that is fired when the event manager's WebSocket connection is closed.
    GuildedWebSocketWelcomeEvent
    Event that is fired when the event manager's WebSocket connection has been opened and successfully logged in.
    ResumeEvent
    Event that is fired when the replay process completes.
    TeamMemberBannedEvent
    Event fired when a server member gets banned.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamMemberBanned
    TeamMemberJoinedEvent
    Event that is fired when a user joins a server.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamMemberJoined
    TeamMemberRemovedEvent
    Event fired when a member is removed from a server.
    TeamMemberUnbannedEvent
    Event fired when a server member is unbanned.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamMemberUnbanned
    TeamMemberUpdatedEvent
    Event fired when a member's nickname is updated.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamMemberUpdated
    TeamRolesUpdatedEvent
    Event fired when one or more member's roles are updated.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/teamRolesUpdated
    TeamWebhookCreatedEvent
    Event fired when a webhook is created.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamWebhookCreated
    TeamWebhookUpdatedEvent
    Event fired when a webhook is updated.
    https://www.guilded.gg/docs/api/websockets/TeamWebhookUpdated
    TeamXpAddedEvent
    Event that is fired when XP is added to user(s).
    UnknownGuildedEvent
    Event that Guilded4J has not implemented or doesn't know how to handle.
